        "background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1B5E20,#66BB6A);"
        "-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent'>"
        "👥 Análise de Cliente — Frota</h2>"
        "<p style='color:#555;font-size:13px;margin:0 0 18px'>"
